<paragraph blockId="24.[136,1451,631,689]" box="[189,1451,631,655]" pageId="24" pageNumber="40">
Description. See Li, Wang &amp; Zhang (2013) for both sexes. Habitus, male palp and epigyne as in 
<figureCitation box="[1223,1357,631,655]" captionStart="Figure 30" captionStartId="24.[155,218,1989,2011]" captionTargetBox="[189,1399,767,1941]" captionTargetId="figure-205@24.[189,1399,767,1941]" captionTargetPageId="24" captionText="Figure 30. Lysania pygmaea Thorell, 1890, male and female from Hainan. A. Male habitus, dorsal view; B. Female habitus, dorsal view; C. Left male palp, bulbus, ventral view; D. Same, retrolateral view; E. Left male palp, ventral view; F. Same, retrolateral view; G. Epigyne, ventral view; H. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–B=0.5mm; C–H=0.1mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5366368" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5366368/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="40">Figs 30A–H</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[1368,1447,631,655]" captionStart="Figure 31" captionStartId="25.[155,218,1049,1071]" captionText="Figure 31. Lysania pygmaea Thorell, 1890, male from Hainan. A. Left male palp, bulbus, ventral view; B–C. Same, retrolateral view. Scale bars=0.04mm." pageId="24" pageNumber="40">31A–C</figureCitation>
,
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="24.[136,1451,631,689]" lastBlockId="25.[136,1451,236,399]" lastPageId="25" lastPageNumber="41" pageId="24" pageNumber="40">
<figureCitation box="[136,218,665,689]" captionStart="Figure 32" captionStartId="25.[155,218,2028,2050]" captionText="Figure 32. Lysania pygmaea Thorell, 1890. A. Left male palp, ventral view; B. Same, retrolateral view; C. Epigyne, ventral view; D. Vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–B=0.2mm; C–D=0.1mm." pageId="24" pageNumber="40">32A–D</figureCitation>
. Material examined. 
<specimenCount box="[401,435,237,261]" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" type="male">1♂</specimenCount>
(
<typeStatus box="[447,542,236,260]" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barrion, Barrion-Dupo &amp; Heong" authorityYear="2012" box="[575,711,237,260]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Pirata" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanya">
<emphasis box="[575,711,237,260]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">Pirata sanya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), Sanya, 
<date box="[809,978,237,261]" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" value="2010-08-09" valueMax="2010-08-13" valueMin="2010-08-09">9–13.VIII.2010</date>
, A.T. Barrion &amp; S.C. Villareal leg. (HANU); 
<specimenCount box="[136,169,271,295]" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" type="female">1♀</specimenCount>
, Bawangling Nature Reserve, 
<date box="[497,630,271,295]" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" value="2007-07-31">31.VII.2007</date>
, F. Zhang leg. (SWUC). Distribution. 
<collectingCountry box="[332,396,306,330]" name="China" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">China</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingRegion box="[409,505,306,330]" country="China" name="Guangxi" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">Guangxi</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[516,596,306,330]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">Hainan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[606,695,306,330]" country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">Yunnan</collectingRegion>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[713,814,306,330]" name="Malaysia" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
. Remarks. Although the types of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1890" box="[529,652,341,364]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Lysania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pygmaea">
<emphasis box="[529,652,341,364]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">L. pygmaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were not examined, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barrion, Barrion-Dupo &amp; Heong" authorityYear="2012" box="[870,1005,341,364]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Pirata" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanya">
<emphasis box="[870,1005,341,364]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">Pirata sanya</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is clearly a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thorell" authorityYear="1890" box="[1328,1451,341,364]" class="Arachnida" family="Lycosidae" genus="Lysania" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="25" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pygmaea">
<emphasis box="[1328,1451,341,364]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="41">L. pygmaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on the descriptions by Lehtinen &amp; Hippa (1979).
</paragraph>
